      <p>
  $(U\psi )(x_1) = \int _ N (K(x_0, x_1) \psi (x_0) dx_0$
$K(x_0,x_1) = \int _ P e^{\frac{i}{\hbar } S[\gamma ]} D\gamma $
$P=\{ \gamma : \gamma (t_0)=x_0, \gamma (t_1)=x_1$} 
 
</p>

